links.title: Netflix's (NASDAQ: NFLX) Q3 Hints at New Normal
links.description: Netflix (NASDAQ: NFLX) released its Q3 earnings yesterday after the bell, and the market didn't like the numbers; shares are set to open down more than 5% today. NFLX had started to pull back over the past five sessions, and today's open will take shares below the 50-day moving average.
